metadata.name: Entrance Music
metadata.description:
Entrance Music 
Amusement Park 
by David Brandon Geeting

An amusement park is a variety show; it is a way to mask a mess. Marrying a discordant blend of studio improvisations, documentary photography, and uncanny portraits, these images navigate through a sketchy trip of frivolous entertainment and hobbyist tinkering, all while threatening to malfunction in the process. Manic and colorful, the manicured world represented in this work is more akin to a comedown than a high. 

Edition: 1 of 1

Fellowship Studio
